312
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,910
but he's gone.

313
00:19:01,750 --> 00:19:02,500
Gone?

314
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:26,520
[Jiahao]

315
00:19:40,340 --> 00:19:42,360
Hello, the number you have dialed is off.

316
00:19:57,450 --> 00:19:58,250
Who was that?

317
00:19:59,940 --> 00:20:01,110
Why didn't you answer the phone?

318
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:03,520
Is it someone from the He family?

319
00:20:06,170 --> 00:20:07,040
Why are you here?

320
00:20:07,760 --> 00:20:09,010
To see you.

321
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:11,030
