332
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:34,530
is to open a nightclub.

333
00:20:35,520 --> 00:20:36,370
Don't worry.

334
00:20:36,370 --> 00:20:38,860
This time, the business is absolutely reliable.

335
00:20:38,860 --> 00:20:40,280
My friend has said.

336
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:41,920
If I can buy that nightclub,

337
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,000
I'll definitely make a lot of money.

338
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:46,590
