339
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:49,260
My money is yours.

340
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:50,010
I don't have any money.

341
00:20:51,490 --> 00:20:52,900
That's not funny.

342
00:20:53,300 --> 00:20:54,280
When your mom died,

343
00:20:54,940 --> 00:20:56,960
how could she not leave you any money?

344
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:58,220
