345
00:20:58,810 --> 00:21:00,050
Don't think you can pester me

346
00:21:00,050 --> 00:21:00,760
like you pestered my mom.

347
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:02,660
Even if you die,

348
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,690
it's none of my business.

349
00:21:08,820 --> 00:21:09,980
You don't think of me as your father,

350
00:21:10,490 --> 00:21:12,350
but don't you want to join the He family again?

351
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:20,810
Think about it.

352
00:21:21,670 --> 00:21:23,430
If I told them that your mom

353
00:21:23,430 --> 00:21:24,850
