370
00:22:02,580 --> 00:22:03,300
The He family?

371
00:22:04,490 --> 00:22:06,170
I never wanted to go back to the He family.

372
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,040
The He family

373
00:22:09,490 --> 00:22:10,270
and you

374
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:13,290
have nothing to do with me.

375
00:22:41,670 --> 00:22:42,440
Where have you been?

376
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:47,630
