377
00:22:48,050 --> 00:22:48,960
Why are you ignoring me?

378
00:22:50,130 --> 00:22:51,160
What have you got there?

379
00:22:51,650 --> 00:22:52,200
Show me.

380
00:22:52,200 --> 00:22:52,990
