447
00:25:19,760 --> 00:25:20,740
He Jiahao.

448
00:25:21,850 --> 00:25:23,620
You even dare fight at school, huh?

449
00:25:24,450 --> 00:25:25,180
Good.

450
00:25:26,650 --> 00:25:29,200
Ms. Qiu, I'm going to take a leave of absence for Jiahao.

451
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:30,850
