491
00:27:39,050 --> 00:27:39,770
Dad, it's my fault.

492
00:27:39,770 --> 00:27:40,370
His things?

493
00:27:40,370 --> 00:27:41,130
No, Dad.

494
00:27:41,130 --> 00:27:42,690
