549
00:31:08,840 --> 00:31:09,600
but the problem is...

550
00:31:10,790 --> 00:31:11,530
Ms. Qiu.

551
00:31:11,990 --> 00:31:13,010
Jiahao is fine.

552
00:31:13,010 --> 00:31:14,560
He is studying in his room.

553
00:31:16,460 --> 00:31:18,820
